    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention to be roadworthy again. The engine has a persistent knock, and the transmission slips frequently, making it unreliable for daily use. Cosmetically, there are several large dents, significant paint oxidation, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This is an ideal candidate for a complete restoration project or for use as a donor vehicle for parts.",
